"3 tablespoons white balsamic vinegar","1 tablespoon chopped shallots","1 pound baby carrots with tops","1 tablespoon olive oil","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","12  fingerling potatoes, halved lengthwise (about 1 1/4 pounds)","1  (6-ounce) bag radishes, halved (about 1 3/4 cups)","2 cups (2-inch) slices asparagus (about 1 pound)","1 tablespoon chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1 tablespoon chopped fresh chives"